<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<title>订单确认</title>
		<style>
			body {
				font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: #333;
				max-width: 800px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 20px;
			}
			.header {
				background-color: #FFD700;
				padding: 20px;
				text-align: center;
				border-radius: 5px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
			}
			.order-info {
				background-color: #f9f9f9;
				padding: 20px;
				border-radius: 5px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
			}
			table {
				width: 100%;
				border-collapse: collapse;
				margin-top: 20px;
			}
			th,
			td {
				padding: 12px;
				text-align: left;
				border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
			}
			th {
				background-color: #FFF4B8;
			}
			.total {
				font-size: 1.2em;
				font-weight: bold;
				text-align: right;
				padding: 15px 0;
			}
			.footer {
				margin-top: 30px;
				text-align: center;
				color: #666;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="header">
			<h1>订单确认</h1>
		</div>

		<div class="order-info">
			<p>尊敬的
				{{ order.customerName }}：</p>
			<p>感谢您的订购！您的订单已经确认。以下是您的订单详情：</p>

			<h2>订单信息</h2>
			<p>订单号:
				{{ order.id }}</p>
			<p>取货地点:
				{{ order.pickupLocation.name }}</p>
			<p>取货时间:
				{{ order.pickupTime|date('Y-m-d H:i:s') }}</p>
		</div>

		<h2>订单明细</h2>
		<table>
			<thead>
				<tr>
					<th>商品</th>
					<th>数量</th>
					<th>单价</th>
					<th>小计</th>
				</tr>
			</thead>
			<tbody>
				{% for item in order.orderItems %}
					<tr>
						<td>{{ item.product.name }}</td>
						<td>{{ item.quantity }}</td>
						<td>€{{ item.price }}</td>
						<td>€{{ item.price * item.quantity }}</td>
					</tr>
				{% endfor %}
			</tbody>
		</table>

		<div class="total">
			总计: €{{ order.totalAmount }}
		</div>

		<div class="footer">
			<p>如有任何问题，请随时联系我们。</p>
			<p>电话：XXX-XXXX-XXXX</p>
			<p>邮箱：{{ adminEmail }}</p>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
